item.title: CVE-2023-0893|2024-08-02T05:24:34.603Z -- unknown -- time%20sheets
item.description: The Time Sheets WordPress plugin before 1.29.3 does not sanitise and escape some of its settings, which could allow high privilege users such as admin to perform Stored Cross-Site Scripting attacks even when the unfiltered_html capability is disallowed (for example in multisite setup)
